thread.title: BRIEF-Liaoning Cheng Da issues 2018 first tranche super short-term financing notes worth 1 bln yuan

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Liaoning Cheng Da issues 2018 first tranche super short-term financing notes worth 1 bln yuan

organizations.name: reuters) - liaoning cheng da co ltd

text:
Jan 11 (Reuters) - Liaoning Cheng Da Co Ltd
* Says it issued 2018 first tranche super short-term financing notes worth 1 billion yuan with a term of 264 days, and coupon rate of 5.6 percent
